title: Week 3 preview & Texans vs. Patriots recap
itunes:title: Week 3 preview & Texans vs. Patriots recap
description:
A room filled with heroes - Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal, Chris Wesseling, and Marc Sessler – go game-by-game breaking down each Week 3 matchup, and reveal which team is their “Lock of the Week”. Plus, the heroes recap the Thursday night game between the Houston Texans and the New England Patriots that featured rookie quarterback Jacoby Brissett (aka Jake Brisket) in his first NFL start.
